τος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Πίδοσσα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Πίδοσσα\">Πίδοσσα\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Πάρωνος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Πάρων\">Πάρωνος\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">τοῦ\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Ἐπιάνακτος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Ἐπιάναξ\">Ἐπιάνακτος\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πίδοσσα Πάρωνος\n                    τοῦ Ἐπιάνακτος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πίδοσσα\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πίδοσσα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Πίδοσσα\">ΠΙΔΟΣΣΑ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πάρωνος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πάρωνος\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πάρωνος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Πάρων\">ΠΑΡΩΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἐπιάνακτος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἐπιάνακτος\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ἐπιάνακτος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Ἐπιάναξ\">ΕΠΙΑΝΑΚΤΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πίδοσσα\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Πίδοσσα\">ΠΙΔΟΣΣΑ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Πάρωνος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Πάρων\">ΠΑΡΩΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"τοῦ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Ἐπιάνακτος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Ἐπιάναξ\">ΕΠΙΑΝΑΚΤΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001244_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001244_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001244.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001244-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text of Gualtherus and Franz\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Kaibel: [..]πιδος Σα[ρ]α[πί]ωνος. The suggestion of a lacuna at the start of the line is entirely speculative on the part of Kaibel.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Gualtherus marks a '.' between the two words, but whether this is intended to signify an interpunct or a missing character is unclear.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The text appears to be on a relief, possibly funerary, of which Gualtherus provides a drawing. There is no record of autopsy after Gualtherus and it appears to be lost. Kaibel's attempt to suggest a comprehensible text ignores the presentation of Gualtherus; Kaibel's reference to Gualtherus fails to indicate that the text is in the addenda, p.100, not the main sequence.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] add. no. 3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Castelli 1769 180 cl. 14 no. 96 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Castelli 1784 cl. 14 no. 110 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Franz 1853 5630 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">417\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[231,234,237,240,243,246,249,252],{"id":232,"html":